User Input (vCPU, Memory, Region, OS, Duration, Type)
        │
        ▼
Candidate Generator (filter instance types)
        │
        ▼
Price Fetcher (your EC2 pricing tool logic)
        │
        ▼
Scoring Engine (rank by price + performance)
        │
        ▼
Recommendation Output (top 3 instances + pricing tier)
